---
import Layout from '~/layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = 'April 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy — Mirage Interactive Ltd"
  description="How the Mirage Interactive website handles data. Short version: it doesn't."
  canonical="https://mirageinteractive.uk/privacy"
>
  <main class="container-page py-20">
    <a href="/" class="text-sm text-ink-400 hover:text-white">&larr; Home</a>
    <h1 class="mt-6 font-display text-4xl font-bold text-white sm:text-5xl">Privacy policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-ink-400">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="mt-10 max-w-2xl space-y-6 text-ink-200">
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Scope</h2>
      <p>This policy applies to the <code class="font-mono text-sm text-mi-200">mirageinteractive.uk</code> website only. Each Mirage product has its own privacy policy, linked from the product's own site.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">What this site collects</h2>
      <p>Aside from the product waitlists described below, this website does not ask you for any information. We do not run Google Analytics, social pixels, or third-party trackers. We do not set cookies for analytics or marketing.</p>
      <p>We may use Cloudflare Web Analytics, which counts page hits by path and country without setting cookies or fingerprinting visitors.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Product waitlists</h2>
      <p>If you join a product waitlist (e.g. Mirage Lumen), we store the email address you submit and the time you submitted it, in a Cloudflare KV namespace, so that we can email you when the product ships. We do not use this address for anything else. You can request deletion at any time by emailing <a href="mailto:legal@mirageinteractive.uk" class="text-mi-200 hover:text-white">legal@mirageinteractive.uk</a>; we will delete within 30 days and confirm.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">If you email us</h2>
      <p>Emails sent to any <code class="font-mono text-sm text-mi-200">@mirageinteractive.uk</code> address are received via Cloudflare Email Routing and handled in Proton Mail. We retain correspondence only as long as it is useful to do so, and we do not share it with third parties outside of lawful requests.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Your rights (UK GDPR)</h2>
      <p>You have the right to access, correct, or delete personal data we hold about you. Email <a href="mailto:legal@mirageinteractive.uk" class="text-mi-200 hover:text-white">legal@mirageinteractive.uk</a> and we will respond within 30 days.</p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Controller</h2>
      <p>Data controller: Mirage Interactive Ltd (company number SC794383), registered in Scotland. Registered office: 48 West George Street, Clyde Offices, 2nd Floor, Glasgow G2 1BP.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
